                           and more  PageMaker including versions 
                           versions of Lorem IpsumeMak
                           versions of Lorem IpsumeMaker including versions 
                           versions of Lorem Ipsum."
                           Margin="5,0,5,0">
                    </Label>
                </StackLayout>
            </Frame>
